title: Ki's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Ki's, the "i" pronounced long "i," features some vegetarian and vegan-friendly choices on its breakfast/lunch menu, which includes a marinated tempeh sandwich, vegetable stir fry, fajitas, tostada, veggie millet burger, butternut squash and corn enchiladas, fresh juices and smoothies. Breakfast/lunch is priced reasonable and inexpensive - you order at the counter and food is brought to your table. Dinner menu has fish in addition to veg-options and is full service. Seating is on 2nd floor with ocean view.
